  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and somehow she worked also for-- for-- for industry, but always under the-- she must have had some kind of a protection by some higher ups that she thought she could survive.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Alice and Lotta.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The nurse was Lotta, and the other one was Alice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Schloss.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother brother-- you know, my mother's maiden name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six and a half years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Italy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] We came-- we came with him in-- we came to Italy with the invasion in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Drive-- we were driving trucks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were a company of-- of trucks-- truckers, you know, a transportation company.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One time, and I worked-- I [? went ?] a-- a machine there for anti-aircraft in Tobruk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- see, in Tobruk we had-- it was at a time of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the British, we are-- we were driven out of Crete by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Churchill had sent all the armaments to Greece and had neglected North Africa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE]-- the-- the British Army [INAUDIBLE] the Italians from North Africa and had taken Tobruk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the-- and the army was left with only small amounts of equipment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So in-- in Tobruk, when Tobruk, was taken, mainly by Australians, they took out the mines.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Tobruk was surrounded by mines, the minefields.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Australians got out of the mines and-- and demobilized them, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I worked with them with my truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Germans-- Germans returned and advanced again and-- and-- and laid siege to Trobuk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They took the same mines, the Italian mines, and put them back at the same place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then there were-- the-- on the aircraft, the [? auto ?] was used, the [INAUDIBLE], the original [INAUDIBLE] on the aircraft was partly used.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
